cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to determine the readability of documents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also extensively uses neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves classification tasks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper mentions transferability across languages, which could also make it relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
